-- =============================================================================
-- §19. TESTING SPECIFICATION (C1-C8 Gold Standard)
-- =============================================================================
--
-- Math gates (ALL must pass):
--   Shannon Entropy H >= 2.5 bits  (config.shannon_entropy_min)
--   CCM >= 0.90                     (config.ccm_min)
--   ITQS >= 0.85                    (config.itqs_min)
--   D_EA <= 10%                     (config.dea_max)
--
-- C1 Page Structure (weight 1.0):
--   Each page renders without error; element count >= 5 (config.min_lustre_elements)
--
-- C2 Status Badges (weight 1.5):
--   healthy / degraded / critical all rendered per page that exposes HealthStatus
--
-- C3 Data Grids (weight 1.0):
--   Rows >= 3, columns >= 3 (config.min_grid_rows / config.min_grid_cols)
--   Pages: health_grid, agents, podman, federation, kms, smriti
--
-- C4 Timeline (weight 0.8):
--   Events in ascending timestamp order; validation: telemetry, verification, immune
--
-- C5 Interactive (weight 1.2):
--   Button click → model state change verified in test
--   Pages: cockpit_view (alarm ack), podman (start/stop), immune (toggle_mara)
--
-- C6 Media/Rich (weight 0.8):
--   SVG topology renders (zenoh_mesh, holon, knowledge graph)
--
-- C7 AI Advisory (weight 1.5):
--   AG-UI events flow end-to-end: planning_dashboard AgUiEvent → Zenoh span observed
--   zenoh_test_observer.gleam verifies message received on indrajaal/otel/spans/**
--
-- C8 Action Button (weight 3.0):
--   Safety gates pass before actuation; Guardian approval obtained
--   Verified: SingularityUpdated, StartContainer, AttackDetected escalation
--   2oo3 consensus required (SC-SIL4-006)
--
-- Regression suite: test/comprehensive_ui_regression_test.gleam
--   381 tests, 24 pages x 8 fractal layers, 30s monitoring per page (SC-GLM-TST-002)
--   Zenoh message verification active for every test run (SC-GLM-ZEN-002)

-- =============================================================================
-- §20. MATHEMATICAL STRUCTURES
-- =============================================================================
--
-- Shannon Entropy: H = -Σ p_i log2(p_i)  file: testing/coverage_math.gleam
-- CCM (Cyclomatic): M = E - N + 2P      file: testing/coverage_math.gleam
-- ITQS: weighted mean of C1-C8 scores   file: testing/coverage_math.gleam  threshold: 0.85
-- D_EA: |EXPECTED △ AS_IS| / |EXPECTED ∪ AS_IS|  file: testing/alignment.gleam

